data.description: Come home to Truro at 'The Fish House'' where you step back in time once you come through the door.  This rustic and charming, 1932 beach cottage is a single family residence set right across the road from Corn Hill Beach with wide open living space downstairs and three bedrooms plus a bonus room above.  There is potential for water views from the second floor and a three bedroom, alternative septic system has been designed for the buyer to install with a new well already in place.   Ready for a new chapter, here is your opportunity to hang your hat and head to the beach!
